{"id": "art-7", "label": "Art. 7", "title": "Art. 7", "slug": "art-7", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 7 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>Actul\nconstitutiv al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> în nume colectiv,\nîn comandit&#259; simpl&#259; sau cu r&#259;spundere limitat&#259; va cuprinde:</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1891877117\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2544\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1891877117\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)datele de identificare a <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>;\nla societatea în comandit&#259; simpl&#259; se vor ar&#259;ta <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>comandita&#355;i</span>;</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1833144440\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2543\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1833144440\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)forma, denumirea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> sediul\nsocial;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>c)obiectul\nde activitate al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, cu precizarea\ndomeniului <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> a <span class=SpellE>activit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nprincipale;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_769493096\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2542\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_769493096\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)capitalul social subscris, cu <span class=SpellE>men&#355;ionarea</span>\naportului fiec&#259;rui asociat, în numerar sau în natur&#259;, valoarea\naportului în natur&#259;, modul evalu&#259;rii acestuia; la <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\ncu r&#259;spundere limitat&#259; se vor preciza num&#259;rul <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> valoarea nominal&#259; a <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span>\nsociale, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> num&#259;rul <span\nclass=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sociale atribuite fiec&#259;rui asociat\npentru aportul s&#259;u;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_315900640\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2541\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_315900640\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d<sup>1</sup>)modalitatea de adoptare a hot&#259;rârilor\nadun&#259;rii generale a <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>, cu votul\ntuturor <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>, în cazul în care,\ndatorit&#259; <span class=SpellE>parit&#259;&#355;ii</span> particip&#259;rii\nla capitalul social, nu poate fi stabilit&#259; o majoritate absolut&#259;;</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1575699604\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2540\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1575699604\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)<span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> care\nreprezint&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> administreaz&#259; societatea\nsau administratorii <span class=SpellE>neasocia&#355;i</span>, datele lor de\nidentificare, durata mandatului, puterile ce li s-au conferit <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> dac&#259; ei urmeaz&#259; s&#259; le exercite\nîmpreun&#259; sau separat;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1227445240\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2539\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1227445240\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e<sup>1</sup>)în cazul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\ncu r&#259;spundere limitat&#259;, dac&#259; sunt <span class=SpellE>numi&#355;i</span>\ncenzori sau auditor financiar, datele de identificare ale primilor cenzori,\nrespectiv ale primului auditor financiar;</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>f)partea\nfiec&#259;rui asociat la beneficii <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> la\npierderi;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_668523197\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2538\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_668523197\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f<sup>1</sup>)</span><s><span style='color:#E51C23'>dup&#259;\ncaz, acolo unde legea prevede, datele de identificare a beneficiarilor reali <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> a <span class=SpellE>modalit&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nîn care se exercit&#259; controlul asupra <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span></s><br>\n<br>\n<u><span style='color:#569748'>[textul din Art. 7, litera F^1. din titlul II,\ncapitolul I a fost abrogat la 06-dec-2024 de Art. 1, punctul 1. din <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> 299/2024]</span></u></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>g)sediile\nsecundare - sucursale, <span class=SpellE>agen&#355;ii</span>, <span\nclass=SpellE>reprezentan&#355;e</span> sau alte asemenea <span class=SpellE>unit&#259;&#355;i</span>\nf&#259;r&#259; personalitate juridic&#259; -, atunci când se <span\nclass=SpellE>înfiin&#355;eaz&#259;</span> o dat&#259; cu societatea, sau <span\nclass=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span> pentru <span class=SpellE>înfiin&#355;area</span>\nlor ulterioar&#259;, dac&#259; se are în vedere o atare <span class=SpellE>înfiin&#355;are</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>h)durata\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_21821247\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2537\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_21821247\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>i)modul de dizolvare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de\nlichidare a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>; <span class=SpellE>modalit&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nde asigurare a stingerii pasivului sau de regularizare a lui în acord cu\ncreditorii, în cazul dizolv&#259;rii f&#259;r&#259; lichidare, atunci când <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> sunt de acord cu privire la repartizarea <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> lichidarea patrimoniului <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}